          <p class="light">Record when you reach out to donors so you stay organized and on track to reach your fundraising goals.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col s12 m4">
        <div class="icon-block">
          <h2 class="center blue-grey-text"><i class="material-icons">group</i></h2>
          <h5 class="center">Teamwork Wins</h5>
          <p class="light">Auctionary fosters collaboration between volunteers and nonprofit staff by making it easier to see your team's progress.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col s12 m4">
        <div class="icon-block">
          <h2 class="center blue-grey-text"><i class="material-icons">settings</i></h2>
          <h5 class="center">Easy to Use</h5>
          <p class="light">Designed with user experience in mind, Auctionary is simple to use for all computer skill levels.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

